{"tid":1520786,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全部人上Twitter 用  #LIHKG 聯絡 + Twitter 快速上手法","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T03:46:40.000Z","uid":25909,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"18e1fb5280c16f6bfd381bb573475de9e34d03b9","tid":1520786,"uid":25909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 快速上手法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 用新開 email 登記 <a href=\"http://Twitter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTwitter.com&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2cwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=ad48fccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Twitter.com</a><br />\n2. Follow 連登戶口 (有個假的小心，用以下呢個 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lihkg_forum/status/1167617757027827712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flihkg_forum%2Fstatus%2F1167617757027827712&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2cwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=b928df7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flihkg_forum%2Fstatus%2F1167617757027827712&h=628f4187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lihkg_forum/status/1167617757027827712</a><br />\n3. Follow 哂有 reply 以上呢個 post 的人<br />\n4. 開始出 Post 或者 Retweet with Comments，記得加以下的 Tag，唔好多過 4 個，大細階無所謂的：<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n#FreedomHK<br />\n#HongKongProtests<br />\n#LIHKG<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n5. 唔好只講 Protest 嘢，當佢 IG/Facebook 咁用<br />\n6. 叫哂你啲朋友跟你咁做</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f4a730c1f0f4fabb91fbb95f152a1896147a33e8","tid":1520786,"uid":35842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdMVZe3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdMVZe3.gif&h=dfb69189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ffb1fc3176baaa53337cb15ebbc484081d393ae","tid":1520786,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0